<strong>5 Endings</strong> (4 Bad Endings &amp; 1 True Culprit Ending)<br>- <strong>Unlockable Gallery</strong> encompassing CG art, misc. art, bonus scenes &amp; diary entries<br>- <strong>Original Soundtrack</strong> consisting of 21 unique tracks, as well as a couple of variations<br>- <strong>150,000</strong>+ words in length<br>- <strong>8-10 hours</strong> of playtime, depending on your reading speed and how thorough you are",
